<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="h-full bg-slate-950">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Página no encontrada - RifaGo</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-full px-6 py-12 text-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Neon Background Glows -->
  <div class="absolute -top-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -right-40 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-md w-full space-y-6">
    <!-- Icon Container with Glow -->
    <div class="inline-flex w-24 h-24 rounded-3xl bg-slate-900/80 border border-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-xl shadow-primary/5">
      <span class="text-5xl animate-pulse">🔍</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Error Code -->
    <h1 class="text-8xl md:text-9xl font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-indigo-400 tracking-tight leading-none">
      404
    </h1>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">
      Página no encontrada
    </h2>

    <!-- Description -->
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
      Lo sentimos, el enlace que seguiste no existe, está desactualizado o se ha movido temporalmente.
    </p>

    <!-- Action Buttons -->
    <div class="pt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-light rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/30 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer">
        Volver al Inicio
      </a>
      <button onclick="history.back()" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-slate-300 bg-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-800/80 hover:text-white rounded-2xl transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer">
        Volver Atrás
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
